KEGG annotation (kegg_pathway) of genes as template data.

Source: R/kegg_anno.R
kegg_anno.Rd

KEGG annotation (kegg_pathway) of genes as template data.

Usage

data(kegg_anno)

Format

Dataframe: include columns (id, kegg_pathway), symbol ";" split ko pathways.

References

https://github.com/BioSciTools/BioSciToolsDatasets/tree/main/KEGGenrichBar/

Author

benben-miao

Examples

# 1. Library TOmicsVis package
library(TOmicsVis)

# 2. Load example data
data(kegg_anno)

# 3. View example data
kegg_anno
